    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small dishes used by an individual diner to hold a pat or small serving of butter. For dishes intended to hold and serve butter at the table use "butter dishes (serving dishes)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
